Kin Shriner https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kin_Shriner 0 Kin Shriner (born December 6, 1953) is an American actor, best known for his portrayal of Scott Baldwin on the ABC soap opera General Hospital and its spin-off Port Charles.
